{{wikipedia|Alexander (disambiguation)}}
==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin '''Alexander''', Romanization of Greek [[Αλέξανδρος]], compounded from [[αλέξω]] ("to [[defend]]") and [[ανδρός]], genitive of [[ανήρ]] ("[[man]]"): ''defender of men''.

===Proper noun===
'''Alexander''' (''plural:'' [[Alexanders]])

# A male [[given name]].
#often refers to [[Wikipedia:Alexander the Great|Alexander the Great]].
